{'id': 9968343, 'body': 'Hey Dave, thank you so much for the nice review. It means so much to have you part of this community of change-makers around the world. All I can say is that we promise to work super hard to deliver an even better experience with every new release. Stay tuned!

All the best,
Vikas', 'modified': '2019-08-02T04:36:11Z'}

{'id': 10136933, 'body': "Hey there, we're so happy you found us too! Thank you so much for taking the time to help build our community and make an impact for others. Working together we have a real shot of improving food systems and sustainability across the world. If there's anything I can do to improve the experience for you please don't hesitate to reach out on the app, my username is @vikas

All the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-13T02:03:44Z'}

{'id': 9968359, 'body': "Hey there, thank you so much for the great review. It's thanks to members like you that we have a chance to make an impact in this world and build something that creates value for the community. Thank you for contributing and helping us make it better. We have a lot of great features in store coming soon.

Wishing you the very best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T04:39:35Z'}

{'id': 10674947, 'body': "Hi there, thank you so much for this positive review. We're working hard to make the experience as great as Instagram and one day hopefully even better. Thank you for making our day with this review. Truly grateful.

All the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-09-14T04:38:54Z'}

{'id': 9967425, 'body': "Hi there, thank you so much for the review and great feedback. In the next couple of updates slated in the next 4-6 weeks you'll see a big improvement in the location based searches available in the app. We're taking the approach of building an authentic community, so the results you see have been added by the community rather than by us aggregating from other online sources. We're a year old, and while in 90 countries and the US being the biggest one, it's still a very big place. I hope you'll consider contributing to helping build the community by posting a few reviews.

Thanks so much,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T03:03:04Z'}

{'id': 10136768, 'body': "Hi there thanks very much for the feedback. Our platform is being built on genuine member reviews rather than plugging in a bunch of content from other online sources. We're a year old and just crossed 50k reviews, which means in some places in the world we have a ton of reviews but in others you might be the first person. Try posting a review of your favorite vegan dish near you and then you'll see it pop up in the map. If that's too much for you, it's ok, we understand, and hope you'll come back in a few months and see more relevant content that others have posted. Thanks very much for the feedback.

All the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-13T01:50:23Z'}

{'id': 12736471, 'body': "Wow, thank you so much! We couldn't do what we're doing without the help and support of members in our community like you. Thank you for joining and contributing in helping build the movement. We have big updates to the app coming this month so remember to keep it updated and let us know what you think!

All the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2020-01-06T02:38:32Z'}

{'id': 9968409, 'body': "Hey there thank you so much for the wonderful review. It's only because of members like you that we have a chance to build this movement and make an impact. I'm so encouraged to hear how people are using the platform, what they like, what they don't and see how we can improve. There are so many exciting features in the works to make the platform even better for you.

Wishing you the very best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2021-07-12T01:32:38Z'}

{'id': 10136971, 'body': "Hey there, thank you so much for the kind review. We're grateful for all the amazing reviews and for you helping build our community of change makers across the world working to improve food systems and sustainability.

Wishing you all the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-13T02:06:07Z'}

{'id': 10137065, 'body': "Hi there SPG, thank you so much for the amazing review. We're working hard to make the experience great for you and all of our other members. If there's anything we can do to make the platform better, please reach out to me on the app @vikas

All the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-13T02:13:34Z'}

{'id': 11273030, 'body': "Hey there, thank you so much for the really generous review. It means so much to get feedback like this. We're working hard and know that the app isn't perfect, and we're working hard to make it a success for the community and build a movement around it. It's only going to happen with your continued support, and we're grateful for that.

Wishing you all the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-10-16T03:04:05Z'}

{'id': 12145233, 'body': "Hey there, thank you so much for the positive review. I'm happy to hear that you're loving the app. We have a long way to go in creating the impact that we all want and it's only going to happen with amazing members in our community like you.

Wishing you all the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-12-02T01:35:29Z'}

{'id': 9968209, 'body': "You are amazing! Thank you for taking the time to post a review here. It means so much to us to have members that are helping create change and impact for the animals and organizations like Animal Place. If there's anything we can do to support or make it better, please reach out to me directly at vikas@abillionveg.com

Thanks,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T04:14:37Z'}

{'id': 9967576, 'body': 'Thank you Claire, we love your reviews on the app!

All the best,
Vikas', 'modified': '2019-08-02T03:09:47Z'}

{'id': 9968528, 'body': "I'm so sorry for this. We had a small bug that we fixed, I hope the app ended up downloading and working for you. If you have any concerns please email me at vikas@abillionveg.com

All the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T04:56:52Z'}

{'id': 11524450, 'body': 'Hi there, thanks for the review but what you're saying isn't true. A simple search for "Seattle" will show more than 100 vegan dishes listed and reviewed across the city. We're trying to replicate your results but cannot, perhaps you don't have the right country selected?

Wishing you all the best,
Vikas', 'modified': '2019-10-29T04:10:22Z'}

{'id': 9967600, 'body': "Hi there, I'm so sorry to hear that you're having issues with the app. Could you check if you have upgraded to the latest release please? We have a couple of bugs in the latest production that we're working to fix and I hope we can resolve the lags for you soon.

Wishing you all the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T03:10:53Z'}

{'id': 9967444, 'body': "Hi there, thanks for the feedback. We're taking the approach of building the platform and community from the ground up. We know that's not for everyone and some of you want to see something that's fully built out with lots of options displayed. I hope in a year we'll provide a lot more value to you. Until then wishing you all the best.

Thanks,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T03:04:17Z'}

{'id': 9968486, 'body': "Hey Foxxy, thank you so much for the great review! If there's anything we can do to make the experience better for you please let me know anytime at vikas@abillionveg.com

Thanks & all the best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T04:52:56Z'}

{'id': 9968535, 'body': "Hey there, thanks so much for your feedback. Last November we probably had very options but we've been growing and now we've got lots of amazing vegan dishes reviewed by members all across Seattle. I hope we can get you back to the platform to take it for another spin!

Wishing you the very best,
Vikas", 'modified': '2019-08-02T04:58:25Z'}

{'id': 10137003, 'body': 'Thank you, you rock for posting this review and helping build the community!

All the best,
Vikas', 'modified': '2019-08-13T02:07:38Z'}

